title: CatIntro
position: 318,-2
---
My heart is hammering. I can't tell if I'm breathing. There's... something that isn't human. Something that's <i>talking to me</i>.
You: Here goes nothing...
<<show_character Cat Sad right>>
<<start_voice_blip Cat>>
<<play_music CatTheme 0.5>>
???: Hello! See your signal! You okay? You... not hurt?
I stare. My brain refuses to process the words. That voice. It's real. This is really happening.
???: I hear you. So... you are... <i>human</i>? Real human? From Earth?
    -> ...What?
    -> A cat?
        <<positive_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catLikesYou += 1>>
        <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
        ???: Oh! Cat! Those cute things. You say... nice thing? Thank? Thank you!
        <<show_character Cat Sad right>>
        ???: But you okay, yes? You look... alone. Many alone.
            -> Yeah, I'm fine.
                <<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
                ???: Okay, good. I am... relief? Relieved. Yes.
            -> Not really.
                <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
                ???: Oh. Space is... lonely place. I know this.
            -> (scream in confusion)
                <<stop_voice_blip Cat>>
                I can't help it... I take a deep breath, and...
                You: AAAAAAHHHHHHHH!!!
                <<negative_indicator Cat>>
                <<set $catDislikesYou += 1>>
                <<show_character Cat Surprised right>>
                The creature on the monitor flinches back, ears flattening.
                <<start_voice_blip Cat>>
                ???: AH! So loud! My ears... they very sensitive!
                <<show_character Cat Sad right>>
                ???: Please... next time more quiet? I not mean scare you...
I'm still reeling. An alien, asking if I'm okay. My hands are shaking.
<<start_voice_blip Cat>>
<<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
???: You not look in danger. So... what you do in space? Why you here?
    -> What <i>are</i> you?
        <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
        <<negative_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catDislikesYou += 1>>
        ???: That... not kind. Rude.
        ???: We both life. We both in space. I just... curious.
    -> Who... what... are you?
    -> Why do you want to know?
        <<negative_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catDislikesYou += 1>>
        <<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
        ???: Sorry. I just... want know. I only small... two orbit old? So many thing I not understand yet.
<<show_character Cat Happy right>>
???: Before more question... you have name? What I call you? Human have this, one word for each? So interesting to me!
My mouth is dry. It's asking for my name. It wants to know what to call me. I'm having a conversation with an alien. I'm having a conversation with an <i>alien</i>.
???: I want remember you. Please?
    -> My name's {$playerName}.
        <<show_character Cat Happy right>>
        <<set $catLikesYou += 1>>
        <<positive_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catKnowsPlayerName = true>>
        <<set $catThinksPlayerNameIs = $playerName>>
        <<if $playerName == "Dipper">>
            ???: {$playerName}? Like the star? So cute! I like.
        <<else>>
            ???: {$playerName}! I like this sound. Nice to meet, {$playerName}!
        <<endif>>
    -> I don't know you...
        <<show_character Cat Sad right>>
        <<negative_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catDislikesYou += 1>>
        ???: Oh. Okay. I... too fast? Sorry.
        <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
        ???: But for talk... something to call you? Anything okay.
        -> It's {$playerName}.
            ???: {$playerName}. Nice. I remember.
            <<set $catThinksPlayerNameIs = $playerName>>
        -> I don't have a name.
            <<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
            ???: No name? How other human call you then?
            <<show_character Cat Flirt right>>
            ???: I call you "Human" maybe. I good at... nickname? Yes.
    -> ...
        ???: Shy? Okay, okay. No problem.
        <<show_character Cat Flirt right>>
        ???: I call you "Human" then. I good at nickname!
<<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
???: So... you really human, yes? From Earth? I hear story... so many story! I never see one before!
I'm still trying to wrap my head around this. It's excited. It's <i>excited</i> to meet a human. Like I'm some kind of... celebrity. Or a rare animal.
???: Human have two leg? And thumb? The... the grabby finger? So many thing I want ask!
-> Yeah, it's pretty cool.
    <<show_character Cat Happy2 right>>
    <<set $catLikesYou += 1>>
