    -> What should I call you? Do you have a name?
        <<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
        ???: Name? For me? We... we not have this. One word for one person? My people not do that. We know each other by... by smell, by sound. By who we are.
        <<show_character Cat Happy right>>
        ???: But you have name! So interesting! So I... I make one! For you to say! Yes!
        ???: I am... I am Gnarp! Gnarp! You can call Gnarp!
        <<set $catName = "Gnarp">>
        <<show_character Cat Happy2 right>>
        {$catName}: I like it! I am Gnarp now!
    -> Meowdy.
        <<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
        ???: Meowdy? What is... oh! Greeting! Interesting!
        <<show_character Cat Flirt right>>
        <<set $catLikesYou += 1>>
        <<positive_indicator Cat>>
        ???: Meowdy to you also! I like this word.
        ???: But, what I call? You ask my name? We not have. So I make one! I am Gnarp!
        <<set $catName = "Gnarp">>
        {$catName}: Yes. Gnarp. For you to say.
<<show_character Cat Happy right>>
{$catName}: Oh! One more thing. I... I watch you. Long time. Most of your journey to sun? I listen. Your ship, your... talking to yourself? Your reports? I learn little bit of your words. Your English.
<<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
{$catName}: Is not perfect, I know. Sorry. But I try. I want to say hello proper when I finally call.
<<show_character Cat Happy right>>
{$catName}: So! You careful here. Space is... dangerous. Many danger.
<<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
{$catName}: Why you here? Why not stay on Earth? Your home?
    -> Escaping it all, I guess.
        <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
        <<positive_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catLikesYou += 1>>
        {$catName}: I understand. Sometimes... need get away. I understand.
    -> Exploring the cosmos.
        <<negative_indicator Cat>>
        <<set $catDislikesYou += 1>>
        <<show_character Cat Sad right>>
        {$catName}: Oh. You risk life for... look at space? So brave. Maybe little... crazy? Too.
        <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
    -> I'm... not sure.
        <<show_character Cat Thinking right>>
        {$catName}: Okay. Not sure okay. Sometime we not know. But find safe place good idea. Here very... unpredictable.
<<show_character Cat Surprised right>>
A sound from their end... scuffling, something heavy shifting. A low voice, muffled and indistinct, in the background. {$catName} glances off-screen, ears flattening.
{$catName}: Oh. I... I sorry. I have to go. Now. Sorry!
<<if $catLikesYou >= $catDislikesYou>>
    <<show_character Cat Sad right>>
    {$catName}: But... you ping me, yes? I want talk again, {$catThinksPlayerNameIs}. Sorry, sorry!
    <<show_character Cat Surprised right>>
    {$catName}: I go. Bye!
<<else>>
    <<show_character Cat Neutral right>>
    {$catName}: You take care, {$catThinksPlayerNameIs}. Sorry.
<<endif>>
More shuffling. The feed flickers. {$catName} opens their mouth as if to say something else... then the screen cuts to static.
<<stop_voice_blip Cat>>
<<hide_all_characters>>
<<hide MonitorSilhouette>>
<<show MonitorOn>>
<<play_music MainTheme>>
The transmission cuts off. Whatever was happening on their end, they're gone.
<<set $charactersSecured += 1>>
Your device receives a strange series of pings afterwards, and the screen flickers back to static. {$catName} is gone.
<<jump ThinkingAfterCatLeaves>>
